<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>DailyPaper - 每日论文精选</title>
  {% if latest_date %}<meta http-equiv="refresh" content="0; url={{ base_url }}/{{ latest_date }}/">{% endif %}
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; max-width: 700px; margin: 4rem auto; padding: 0 1rem; color: #1e293b; }
    h1 { color: #2563eb; } a { color: #2563eb; } li { margin: 0.4rem 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>📄 DailyPaper</h1>
  <p>每日自动精选 LLM 安全 / 具身智能安全 / LLM 动态 / 具身智能动态 最值得读的论文。</p>
  {% if latest_date %}<p>正在跳转到最新一期: <a href="{{ base_url }}/{{ latest_date }}/">{{ latest_date }}</a></p>{% endif %}
  <h2>历史归档</h2>
  <ul>{% for date in archive_dates %}<li><a href="{{ base_url }}/{{ date }}/">{{ date }}</a></li>{% endfor %}</ul>
</body>
</html>
